Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.94,0:00:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.71,0:00:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me are the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.67,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd both prefer not to have this power.{I also wish I didn't have this power.} {why did you change this line between episodes}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.77,0:02:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been really heartbreaking for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.05,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a very kind-hearted young man.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred and strife,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this blood-stained world,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{doesn't} they don't suit you.{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.07,0:02:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... Get it over with already.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.34,0:02:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, he's a nuisance for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I leave this to you?{Can I count on you?} {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.98,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to get Ai-chan involved?! {this one's different from episode 2 as well}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.19,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up! I don't wanna see \Nany of that stuff ever again!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm in a bit of a bind, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going down without a fight! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.82,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.91,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back with his friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not stick around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.05,0:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let your family \Nget caught up in it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.20,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Do you want to turn this town into a sea of fire or what?!{Bastard! You wanna plunge the town \Nin the sea of fire, or what?!}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sheathe that sword?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want us to fight bare-handed?{Wanna do it with bare hands?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to my office for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the company?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumihiko-sama, are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamaguchi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have secrets from Sakiya-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.39,0:05:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look, I don't mean to cause you trouble...{L-Look... If you pester me to join you again...} {unsure, maybe "I don't wanna impose or something"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. \NYou got it wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the good guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.32,0:05:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts me... \NIt hurts me just thinking that you...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,got caught up in this.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jump to conclusions. \NYou won't have any doubts after this. {lit: it's to stop you from doing so}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.35,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fragile... Too fragile.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.42,0:05:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That fragility is what pisses me off the most!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.72,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The man’s hysterical—what a sorry sight!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.23,0:06:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the president here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you do realize \Nit's my father's doing. {benefiting from the influence of a master or parent}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,{Well...}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.15,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we {\i1}are{\i0} topping the weekly viewership ratings{after all}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week marked six months \Nsince we rose to that position. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too shoddy, I'd say.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you have me, \Nwouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of serious programs too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's rude! \NWhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've been watching your show.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.00,0:07:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Wow! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Working for the TV is nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.59,0:07:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a busy job.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but sometimes it saves you in return.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give up now.\N You don't have to get up anymore.{Give up already. \NDon't get up.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.24,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I must keep kicking and screaming \Nuntil the end...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.52,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're probably too strong \Nfor me to have any hope of winning...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only get... once chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Close one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost had{ got} me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.65,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that it was you \Nwho broke{violated} the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear them? \NThe footsteps of your buddies.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If only they had come a little sooner!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.65,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Mizusawa! {is how I'd do these at least, just don't have them as the same line}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... The effect of the resonance?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Such enormous power?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to my office for now.{I'll go to my office now.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?{Where should we go?} {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.91,Sign,,0,0,0,,{Studio} {I know you're not one to do signs, but some of these seem important enough} {and yeah, this is aligned to scene changes on my end}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-kun? {珈織}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-kun, we're starting!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll change the news anchor.{Change of the news anchor.}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamaguchi will host this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Escort her out at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To the street.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And drive her home.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I've got to fight him...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had to do something...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.44,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I ended up in this sorry state...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all I got for it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking beaten and lame?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to talk, Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is demonic poison that strong? {guessing in youki part}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.88,0:11:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Flame General's Fire \Nis highly concentrated demonic magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some ordinary toxin.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is the detoxifier?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.85,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is none.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.81,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wondered \Nwhat to say when this time comes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.92,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How about "I'll treat Saeko-chan to a delicious dinner next time"?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to anything you like, every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear it, Jyukuro-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave detoxicating to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.52,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a poison only Saeko-san can cleanse.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Feeling better already?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! \NWhy'd you make me say all that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.55,0:12:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Jyukuro-kun asked me to do it, \Nas a penalty for rushing in on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.89,0:12:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing, Mizusawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.08,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate you \Nacting on your own ever again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.94,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life isn't just for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.83,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now's not a good time.{Hey, he's not looking too great.} {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.53,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do,\N bringing that liability here?{What are you going to do \Nabout that bothersome punk?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any good ideas, \NI'm all ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you implying that having him here is dangerous?{Are you trying to say it's dangerous?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{But he's awfully weak!}Look at you, acting all scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try basking in that light of his once.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see how you talk then.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.60,0:13:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See to it that she gets home safely.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you figured it out?{Did I blow my cover?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.81,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me, who have you \Nbeen talking to just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.01,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been talking to someone \Never since we brought you here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.93,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In your head.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.37,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time... \NThis is the first time it's happened to me... {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.25,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So what were you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.76,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I am... Kudo... Kudo Kaoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou! Put everyone in the building to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too sudden!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.67,0:15:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we've got \Nan important {customer}guest coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.06,0:15:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I must welcome him appropriately,\Nwithout any distractions.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and take him back.{I'll come to take him back.}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Do you accept, King Kara?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.18,0:15:56.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,If we fight here, \Nyou're not getting out alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know it too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way now is forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.37,0:16:32.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,Again... Why must you hate and fight each other? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,And nothing else!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this!{That's enough!}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.27,0:16:41.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Stop... stop bothering me!{I... I don't care anymore!} {??? could be "don't bother me anymore"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.24,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun, I need your help, \NI need your power.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"We'll keep you out of it."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"We'll keep you out of it now."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,And yet...{I see.} {??} {それに}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,you're the ones who started the fighting.{So it's you who I fought earlier?} {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you're the brains of that team.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delighted.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to what he feels and what he decides.{What he feels and decides}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What we can do...{is what we can do.} {?????} {idk either, but this makes slightly more sense to me}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.75,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a gutless weakling.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not worth risking our necks.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.97,0:17:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear{know} that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, why don't you just give him back?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.93,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you crave his power that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cowards and weaklings flock together.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Jyukuro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.82,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think your flame \Nwill be the best out there forever?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.25,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Again... They have to fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.89,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be the one...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,who ends it! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.65,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.87,0:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All on your own—how unfriendly!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Mizusawa! \NGet away from him!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He... He...!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Enveloped in the soft light,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to shut yourself away.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.30,0:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! \NAre you also following him, Mizusawa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Ryosuke to be his friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what'll happen to you \Nif you follow me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.61,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryosuke, your perception of this world \Nis different from {the }ordinary people's.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In your eyes, \NI can only see the things you hate.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been tormenting you \Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.17,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something else I want to see there, \Nother than your gripes. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.22,0:19:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look deep inside me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me,\N you can drag me down with you. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.39,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to never give up \Nlooking at the world
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.77,0:19:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you go this far for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because they ordered you to?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.99,0:19:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're following such a dangerous order, \Nyou really are out of your mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not following orders.{Not necessarily.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.45,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one promise I made to Shinobu that I have to keep.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that I won't die.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demonic Ones eat the people.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Celestials Ones eat the demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And fight them too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the Celestial Ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you still run away?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From this power{our own strength}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.10,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,From yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.24,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.24,0:20:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To accept that destiny is Shinobu's job. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.08,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no one can run away from himself. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs you, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as the blade that breeds conflict, \Nbut for your true {lit. other, but who the fuck knows}strength.{another one of your strengths.}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I... Do I really have it in me? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying here...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying here...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.57,0:21:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is good enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.21,0:21:28.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,Don't forget. \NYou're actually all on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.25,0:21:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Sakiya-kun \Nto expose himself to danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.05,0:21:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.01,0:21:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Sakiya-kun \Nto be no longer able to smile even more!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.78,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have awoken?{So you've woken up?} {my read is that this is a double meaning about how he has awoken to his powers (cf the title), so this form, while it reads wrong for the plain waking up meaning, is more fitting}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.37,0:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the weather and news \Nfirst thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, allow me to start \Nwith the weather in the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.50,0:22:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is expected to be generally sunny \Nand calm with no wind.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.75,0:22:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Precipitation probability is 0% \Nfor both morning and afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.30,0:22:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,10% after 6pm.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.39,0:23:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Comment: 10,0:23:06.78,0:23:12.42,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.08,0:00:48.35,Song,,0,0,0,,Come here and open the window {ここにおいで 窓をあけてくれたら\Nめぐりあえる 出会いと約束}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.68,0:00:55.73,Song,,0,0,0,,and we'll meet and make a promise
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.56,0:01:03.55,Song,,0,0,0,,The truth I saw in the corner of the classroom {教室の片隅で見た\Nほんとのこと\Nだれにも言えないリアルもあるさ}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.55,0:01:09.99,Song,,0,0,0,,There are also some real things I can't tell anyone
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.54,Song,,0,0,0,,Searchin' angel night {Searchin' angel night\N扉の奥\N隠れてた愛が\Nflyin' on flyin' out めざめだす\NCallin' birth of light\N優しさだけ\Nとどくよ きみの 心へ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Behind the door
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.38,0:01:22.34,Song,,0,0,0,,The hidden love
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.34,0:01:26.23,Song,,0,0,0,,Flyin' on flyin' out, it's awakening
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.97,Song,,0,0,0,,Callin' birth of light
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.55,0:01:32.24,Song,,0,0,0,,Only kindness
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.74,0:01:40.69,Song,,0,0,0,,Will reach your heart
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.52,0:23:24.31,Song,,0,0,0,,The heat haze of times immemorial\Nreflects the melody of the Milky Way, {太古(いにしえ)の陽炎(かげろう)が\N映(は)ゆる銀河(みなも)の音律(しらべ)\N貴方(あなた)が歩む軌跡(あしどり)\Nその眼差し　永遠を希(もと)め}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.45,0:23:37.44,Song,,0,0,0,,The path you walk, \Nyour gaze, yearning for eternity
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.44,0:23:49.70,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, I've been waiting for you here \Nall this time, all these years {愛しい人よ\N今まで待ち続けたここで}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.70,0:23:58.82,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching you from now on and forever, \Njust as if I'm we're snuggling up, {これからずっと\N見つめてるよ\Nただ寄り添うように\N零(ゼロ)に還ってゆく\Nその日まで}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.82,0:24:06.08,Song,,0,0,0,,until the day you return to zero
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.91,0:24:20.73,Song,,0,0,0,,The pure sunlight filtering through the leaves {清らかな木洩れ陽が\N分かつ　双(ふた)つの世界\N魂の詩(うた)よ　響け\N引き裂かれた　哀しみの焔(ほのお)}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.96,0:24:26.53,Song,,0,0,0,,divides the two worlds
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.72,0:24:39.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Let the song of the soul resonate, \Nthe flames of torn sorrow
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.92,0:24:51.89,Song,,0,0,0,,O gentle times, when I entrust \Nmy wounded heart to you {優しい時よ\Nゆだねよう傷ついた心\N諍(いさか)うよりも\N大事なこと\Nそっと漂うように\N愛が巡ってくる\Nその日まで}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.33,0:24:57.97,Song,,0,0,0,,There are more important things than quarreling,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.97,0:25:08.64,Song,,0,0,0,,floating gently until the day when love comes around
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.55,0:25:42.11,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, I've been waiting for you here \Nall this time, all these years {愛しい人よ\N今まで待ち続けたここで}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.11,0:25:50.88,Song,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll be by your side forever, \Njust as if we're snuggling up {これからずっと\Nそばにいるよ\Nただ寄り添うように\N雫に還ってゆく\Nいつまでも}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.88,0:25:55.47,Song,,0,0,0,,until the day you return to zero, and forever
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.47,0:26:06.99,Song,,0,0,0,,Let's entrust the endless spiral\Nwith the lost child's light {果てぬ螺旋(らせん)\Nゆだねよう迷(まよ)い子の光\N流星たちが\N夜空埋めた\Nそっと夢見るように\N愛が巡ってくる\N……祈り……}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.99,0:26:20.77,Song,,0,0,0,,The shooting stars fill the night sky\NLove comes round softly, just like a dream
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.84,0:26:25.34,Song,,0,0,0,,I pray...
